1
00:00:12,205 --> 00:00:13,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri.</font>

2
00:00:23,505 --> 00:00:25,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who the hell do you think I am?</font>

3
00:00:36,205 --> 00:00:38,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh my God, he kissed me.</font>

4
00:00:40,171 --> 00:00:41,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Me and Uehara...</font>

5
00:00:49,705 --> 00:00:51,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, no...</font>

6
00:00:54,872 --> 00:00:56,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hang on,</font>

7
00:00:56,405 --> 00:00:59,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">he thought I was someone else.</font>

8
00:00:59,405 --> 00:01:03,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's it, it's just a mistake.</font>

9
00:01:05,405 --> 00:01:07,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's nothing to worry about.</font>

10
00:01:14,039 --> 00:01:16,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, who am I kidding?</font>

11
00:01:18,105 --> 00:01:19,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It totally worries me.</font>

12
00:01:20,605 --> 00:01:21,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What should I do?</font>

13
00:01:22,605 --> 00:01:24,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My very first kiss...</font>

14
00:01:31,105 --> 00:01:33,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Because you kicked me,</font>

15
00:01:33,605 --> 00:01:35,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">my stomach turned red.</font>

16
00:01:35,505 --> 00:01:37,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, stay away from me!</font>

17
00:01:39,672 --> 00:01:42,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, what's the matter?</font>

18
00:01:42,205 --> 00:01:44,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're the one who did it, you know.</font>

19
00:01:44,305 --> 00:01:47,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

20
00:01:47,205 --> 00:01:48,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

21
00:01:52,605 --> 00:01:54,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you remember?</font>

22
00:01:54,105 --> 00:01:55,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Remember what?</font>

23
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:58,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If my alarm's going off,
wake me up normally.</font>

24
00:01:58,672 --> 00:02:00,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What do you mean <i>normally?
-Are you daft?</i></font>

25
00:02:01,005 --> 00:02:04,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wake me up gently, OK?</font>

26
00:02:29,105 --> 00:02:31,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no way I can do that?</font>

27
00:03:51,839 --> 00:03:53,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, you.</font>

28
00:03:54,405 --> 00:03:56,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

29
00:03:57,305 --> 00:03:58,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't tell me, after all this time,</font>

30
00:03:59,205 --> 00:04:02,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you're concerned about living with a boy?</font>

31
00:04:05,605 --> 00:04:10,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you fantasizing about me
making a move on you?</font>

32
00:04:13,305 --> 00:04:14,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't worry.</font>

33
00:04:19,972 --> 00:04:23,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have absolutely no interest in you.</font>

34
00:04:25,472 --> 00:04:27,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Put my bag back the way it was,</font>

35
00:04:27,805 --> 00:04:32,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and like I said before,
don't talk to me at school.</font>

36
00:04:42,072 --> 00:04:44,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now I'm ticked off.</font>

37
00:04:46,005 --> 00:04:46,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Darn him!</font>

38
00:05:04,939 --> 00:05:06,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Three meters.</font>

39
00:05:57,205 --> 00:06:01,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Where did Uehara go?</font>

40
00:06:05,305 --> 00:06:07,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait! Where am I?</font>

41
00:06:09,705 --> 00:06:12,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Damn, she's so stupid.</font>

42
00:06:18,805 --> 00:06:20,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Good morning.
-Hi.</font>

43
00:06:20,705 --> 00:06:22,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is Nao having the day off today?</font>

44
00:06:23,705 --> 00:06:28,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I haven't heard anything. Where is she?</font>

45
00:06:28,605 --> 00:06:32,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Today is my big chance to see Uehara.</font>

46
00:06:32,105 --> 00:06:35,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, that's today, huh?</font>

47
00:06:35,205 --> 00:06:36,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yep!</font>

48
00:06:36,905 --> 00:06:39,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What a load of crap.</font>

49
00:06:39,705 --> 00:06:42,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I got a message from Nao.</font>

50
00:06:42,505 --> 00:06:43,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What does it say?</font>

51
00:06:43,972 --> 00:06:46,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She says "I am lost."</font>

52
00:06:46,472 --> 00:06:47,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

53
00:06:51,505 --> 00:06:53,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where am I?</font>

54
00:06:54,072 --> 00:06:56,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm going to be late.</font>

55
00:06:58,572 --> 00:07:00,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh no, it's a dead end.</font>

56
00:07:04,405 --> 00:07:05,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Help! No!</font>

57
00:07:08,305 --> 00:07:09,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Help me!</font>

58
00:07:11,872 --> 00:07:13,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I made it.</font>

59
00:07:17,105 --> 00:07:20,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I had a messed up first kiss from someone</font>

60
00:07:20,405 --> 00:07:22,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">who told me he's not interested in me,</font>

61
00:07:23,105 --> 00:07:25,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and I got chased by a dog!</font>

62
00:07:26,205 --> 00:07:28,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is all, completely, entirely,</font>

63
00:07:28,939 --> 00:07:32,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara's fault!</font>

64
00:07:32,205 --> 00:07:36,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! Be quiet in here!</font>

65
00:07:36,405 --> 00:07:37,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yes, Sir!
-You are late.</font>

66
00:07:38,072 --> 00:07:39,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

67
00:07:39,305 --> 00:07:43,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so sorry, please excuse me.</font>

68
00:07:48,105 --> 00:07:51,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Aren't you going to eat, Nao?</font>

69
00:07:51,672 --> 00:07:54,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think she's run out of energy for today.</font>

70
00:07:54,939 --> 00:07:58,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You followed unknown roads,
moreover, you have no sense of direction!</font>

71
00:07:58,972 --> 00:08:01,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's not my fault, it's...</font>

72
00:08:02,305 --> 00:08:04,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't tell anyone we live together.</font>

73
00:08:07,039 --> 00:08:08,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

74
00:08:09,505 --> 00:08:11,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Actually it's all my fault.</font>

75
00:08:11,472 --> 00:08:13,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, keep your chin up.</font>

76
00:08:13,772 --> 00:08:17,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">After this, we have sports with A class!</font>

77
00:08:17,572 --> 00:08:19,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Joint sports class...</font>

78
00:08:21,405 --> 00:08:24,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, come on, you two. Perk up!</font>

79
00:08:24,805 --> 00:08:28,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We can see Uehara who looks so cool!</font>

80
00:08:28,105 --> 00:08:31,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've seen enough. No thanks.</font>

81
00:08:31,405 --> 00:08:33,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm full.</font>

82
00:08:33,705 --> 00:08:37,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come on, Nao, what are you talking about?</font>

83
00:08:37,105 --> 00:08:38,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Get out of the way!
-Hey! What the...</font>

84
00:08:38,872 --> 00:08:40,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nao, let's go!
-Huh? Why?</font>

85
00:08:40,405 --> 00:08:43,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Quickly now!
-Wait a sec, Marina!</font>

86
00:08:49,505 --> 00:08:53,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Look at that. It's like a fantasy world.</font>

87
00:08:54,005 --> 00:08:56,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's so sharp and cool.</font>

88
00:08:56,205 --> 00:09:00,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But sometimes, he looks so lonely.</font>

89
00:09:00,171 --> 00:09:01,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The shop's sold out of curry bread.</font>

90
00:09:01,605 --> 00:09:02,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

91
00:09:04,805 --> 00:09:06,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did you see that?</font>

92
00:09:06,305 --> 00:09:08,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's just bummed about the curry--</font>

93
00:09:08,072 --> 00:09:11,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It must be because he suffered
while growing up.</font>

94
00:09:12,005 --> 00:09:16,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He is the perfect guy for me.</font>

95
00:09:17,205 --> 00:09:19,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know Uehara lost his parents</font>

96
00:09:19,505 --> 00:09:20,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">when he was a kid, right?</font>

97
00:09:21,705 --> 00:09:23,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm no freeloader you know.</font>

98
00:09:26,072 --> 00:09:27,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, in conclusion,</font>

99
00:09:27,072 --> 00:09:31,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">no matter how many times I see him,</font>

100
00:09:31,472 --> 00:09:34,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">he is the perfect man for me! Uehara!</font>

101
00:09:44,605 --> 00:09:45,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I don't like him.</font>

102
00:09:46,605 --> 00:09:49,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-Oh, nothing, don't worry.</font>

103
00:09:52,605 --> 00:09:55,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you think he has a girlfriend?</font>

104
00:09:55,939 --> 00:09:58,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really? Who told you that?</font>

105
00:10:01,305 --> 00:10:02,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

106
00:10:04,705 --> 00:10:05,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri.</font>

107
00:10:09,605 --> 00:10:14,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, what I meant was that
he must have at least one girlfriend.</font>

108
00:10:14,705 --> 00:10:18,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I haven't heard that rumor yet,</font>

109
00:10:18,605 --> 00:10:22,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but I would be so shocked if he has one.</font>

110
00:10:22,305 --> 00:10:26,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't get to see cool guys like him
so often, you know?</font>

111
00:10:28,305 --> 00:10:30,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't know why he's so popular.</font>

112
00:10:31,105 --> 00:10:33,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He is one of the top three.</font>

113
00:10:33,505 --> 00:10:35,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The <i>rules are so tough too.</i></font>

114
00:10:36,005 --> 00:10:37,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Rules?</i></font>

115
00:10:37,772 --> 00:10:39,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You heard them the other day.</font>

116
00:10:39,905 --> 00:10:41,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>-Remember?
-I remember but...</i></font>

117
00:10:41,405 --> 00:10:44,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>The unspoken rules among girls.</i></font>

118
00:10:44,405 --> 00:10:45,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sit.</font>

119
00:10:47,705 --> 00:10:51,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There are three groups interested in
Uehara at the moment.</font>

120
00:10:53,505 --> 00:10:55,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>First are the teachers' favorites,</i></font>

121
00:10:55,705 --> 00:10:58,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>the super smart girls.</i></font>

122
00:10:58,705 --> 00:11:01,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Next are the really naughty ones,</i></font>

123
00:11:01,105 --> 00:11:03,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>the outlaw girls.</i></font>

124
00:11:03,905 --> 00:11:05,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>And the ones that are popular
with the guys,</i></font>

125
00:11:05,905 --> 00:11:08,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>the manager girls.</i></font>

126
00:11:08,505 --> 00:11:10,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">These three groups decided</font>

127
00:11:11,039 --> 00:11:14,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">to manage all interactions with Uehara.</font>

128
00:11:15,872 --> 00:11:18,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara is for everyone.</font>

129
00:11:19,005 --> 00:11:22,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you talk with him or meet with him,</font>

130
00:11:22,105 --> 00:11:24,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">it can cause big trouble!</font>

131
00:11:24,939 --> 00:11:26,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's like a goddamn national treasure.</font>

132
00:11:27,105 --> 00:11:29,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, national treasure! No touching!</font>

133
00:11:30,205 --> 00:11:31,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, shouldn't you be getting ready?</font>

134
00:11:32,005 --> 00:11:34,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Next lesson is your favorite, right?</font>

135
00:11:34,105 --> 00:11:35,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're right!</font>

136
00:11:36,405 --> 00:11:41,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, no! I kissed the national treasure!</font>

137
00:11:48,705 --> 00:11:52,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, Marina, which group are you in?</font>

138
00:11:52,505 --> 00:11:55,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm just one of the majority.</font>

139
00:11:55,405 --> 00:11:56,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just hope that Uehara</font>

140
00:11:56,805 --> 00:12:00,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">will approach me on his own.</font>

141
00:12:00,872 --> 00:12:02,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, right. Nice imagination!</font>

142
00:12:02,672 --> 00:12:04,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi!</font>

143
00:12:05,205 --> 00:12:08,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">UEHARA</font>

144
00:12:08,305 --> 00:12:09,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What's up?
-What?</font>

145
00:12:13,405 --> 00:12:15,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's nothing.</font>

146
00:12:17,305 --> 00:12:20,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nothing at all. I got to go to the toilet.</font>

147
00:12:20,605 --> 00:12:22,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have a sore tummy.</font>

148
00:12:22,105 --> 00:12:24,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nao?
-Nao?</font>

149
00:12:25,905 --> 00:12:29,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If I get found out...</font>

150
00:12:36,839 --> 00:12:39,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm screwed!</font>

151
00:12:44,105 --> 00:12:47,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey Uehara, help us out next lesson.</font>

152
00:12:47,805 --> 00:12:49,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We don't want to lose to class D.</font>

153
00:12:50,171 --> 00:12:52,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, I'm going to sleep in the infirmary.</font>

154
00:12:57,505 --> 00:13:01,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you know her?
She's looking right at you.</font>

155
00:13:01,772 --> 00:13:04,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nope, no idea.</font>

156
00:13:10,405 --> 00:13:11,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's dancing!</font>

157
00:13:14,705 --> 00:13:16,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe she ate something wrong!</font>

158
00:13:29,305 --> 00:13:30,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You!</font>

159
00:13:31,605 --> 00:13:32,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

160
00:13:34,205 --> 00:13:37,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I told you to stay away from me!</font>

161
00:13:37,405 --> 00:13:39,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's an emergency. Read this!</font>

162
00:13:40,171 --> 00:13:41,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

163
00:13:48,305 --> 00:13:50,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, stop it!</font>

164
00:14:04,005 --> 00:14:06,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks to her, I couldn't play hooky.</font>

165
00:14:07,839 --> 00:14:09,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">YOSHIKAWA</font>

166
00:14:16,772 --> 00:14:18,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where did she go?</font>

167
00:14:24,305 --> 00:14:25,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! Wait!</font>

168
00:14:32,105 --> 00:14:34,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>You've got the wrong sports clothes,
Uehara.</i></font>

169
00:14:34,905 --> 00:14:38,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>There's no one in the home economics room,
so let's swap there.</i></font>

170
00:14:38,705 --> 00:14:40,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's not me, it's your mistake!</font>

171
00:14:44,205 --> 00:14:45,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">UEHARA</font>

172
00:14:48,939 --> 00:14:50,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, wait!</font>

173
00:14:50,605 --> 00:14:52,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stop it!</font>

174
00:14:54,405 --> 00:14:56,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">UEHARA</font>

175
00:15:01,705 --> 00:15:05,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the hell? Why did you cut it?</font>

176
00:15:06,005 --> 00:15:10,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Because you wouldn't listen to me.</font>

177
00:15:12,105 --> 00:15:13,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Fix it!</font>

178
00:15:13,205 --> 00:15:14,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

179
00:15:14,205 --> 00:15:15,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll give you five minutes.</font>

180
00:15:16,672 --> 00:15:18,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's impossible!</font>

181
00:15:18,205 --> 00:15:21,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's just a small hole.</font>

182
00:15:21,939 --> 00:15:24,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's like wearing a pants
with holes in the knees, see?</font>

183
00:15:24,205 --> 00:15:26,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is not the knee, you idiot!</font>

184
00:15:26,605 --> 00:15:29,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no shirts with a hole here!</font>

185
00:15:29,705 --> 00:15:33,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You always get pissed off.</font>

186
00:15:33,472 --> 00:15:34,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the...</font>

187
00:15:35,872 --> 00:15:38,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Fine, I'll fix it.</font>

188
00:15:39,205 --> 00:15:40,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You are such a pain.</font>

189
00:15:41,039 --> 00:15:42,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If only you had listened to me...</font>

190
00:15:43,005 --> 00:15:44,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, this is your fault,</font>

191
00:15:44,705 --> 00:15:47,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and who the hell cuts shirts like this?</font>

192
00:15:47,205 --> 00:15:48,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can't help it now though.</font>

193
00:15:48,939 --> 00:15:51,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No one cuts it like this though.</font>

194
00:15:51,205 --> 00:15:53,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Shut up.</font>

195
00:15:53,205 --> 00:15:55,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Which needle do I use?</font>

196
00:15:55,705 --> 00:15:57,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who cares! Use any of them.</font>

197
00:15:57,672 --> 00:15:58,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I found it.</font>

198
00:16:06,105 --> 00:16:07,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not yet?</font>

199
00:16:07,705 --> 00:16:09,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't rush me, OK?</font>

200
00:16:09,305 --> 00:16:11,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hurry up. You are a girl, right?</font>

201
00:16:12,705 --> 00:16:16,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, that's a stereotype!</font>

202
00:16:16,805 --> 00:16:18,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You were going to sleep
in the infirmary anyway.</font>

203
00:16:19,039 --> 00:16:21,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That has nothing to do with it.</font>

204
00:16:22,005 --> 00:16:23,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What a pain in the ass.</font>

205
00:16:24,205 --> 00:16:25,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What did you say?</font>

206
00:16:26,472 --> 00:16:28,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, nothing.</font>

207
00:16:32,672 --> 00:16:34,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ouch!</font>

208
00:16:34,772 --> 00:16:36,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, are you OK?</font>

209
00:16:38,472 --> 00:16:41,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the hell? It's no big deal.</font>

210
00:16:42,972 --> 00:16:44,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, come on,</font>

211
00:16:44,672 --> 00:16:47,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">what would you do
if a girl got a scar on her hand?</font>

212
00:16:47,405 --> 00:16:48,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A girl?</font>

213
00:16:50,672 --> 00:16:53,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you're a girl, fix this!</font>

214
00:16:53,905 --> 00:16:57,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Shut up, I'm doing it now.</font>

215
00:16:57,305 --> 00:16:59,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You are taking forever.
-Help me then.</font>

216
00:17:12,205 --> 00:17:14,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Strike three! Batter out!</font>

217
00:17:37,872 --> 00:17:39,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Do your best!
-You can do it!</font>

218
00:18:01,105 --> 00:18:03,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Strike! Batter out!</font>

219
00:18:08,772 --> 00:18:11,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Uehara, you're so cool!
-You're awesome!</font>

220
00:18:16,805 --> 00:18:18,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't worry about it, Mitsuichi.</font>

221
00:18:18,705 --> 00:18:21,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's only you coming for me, Nao.</font>

222
00:18:22,005 --> 00:18:24,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Don't say that, it's not true.
-Yes, it is.</font>

223
00:18:24,572 --> 00:18:27,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nao!
-Hi, Daichi.</font>

224
00:18:27,605 --> 00:18:30,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Do you have sports class too, Daichi?
-Yeah.</font>

225
00:18:30,572 --> 00:18:34,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, you are holding the bat wrong.</font>

226
00:18:35,205 --> 00:18:37,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi, can you teach me?</font>

227
00:18:38,105 --> 00:18:42,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to hit him for a home run!</font>

228
00:18:42,105 --> 00:18:45,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-At any cost...
-Wow, that's not like you, Nao.</font>

229
00:18:45,939 --> 00:18:48,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're all feisty.</font>

230
00:18:48,605 --> 00:18:51,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't like him.</font>

231
00:18:51,505 --> 00:18:53,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Just because he's cool,
-You're right.</font>

232
00:18:54,039 --> 00:18:56,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">good at sports and doing well in school,</font>

233
00:18:56,205 --> 00:18:58,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-he thinks he can get away with anything.
-That's right.</font>

234
00:18:58,705 --> 00:19:01,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The world doesn't revolve around you!</font>

235
00:19:01,605 --> 00:19:02,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah! Not you!</font>

236
00:19:07,072 --> 00:19:08,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Hit it!
-I will.</font>

237
00:19:08,105 --> 00:19:12,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nao, you will hit a home run!
-Yep, I will!</font>

238
00:19:12,605 --> 00:19:14,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">First, this is how you hold the bat.</font>

239
00:19:14,505 --> 00:19:15,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK!</font>

240
00:19:16,305 --> 00:19:18,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-OK.
-Left hand at the bottom,</font>

241
00:19:18,305 --> 00:19:19,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-keep your arms in tight.
-OK.</font>

242
00:19:19,805 --> 00:19:20,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-See?
-Yeah.</font>

243
00:19:20,805 --> 00:19:23,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't try to hit it with your bat,
use your whole body.</font>

244
00:19:23,405 --> 00:19:25,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like a spring, unwind and hit!</font>

245
00:19:30,839 --> 00:19:32,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Strike!</font>

246
00:19:39,905 --> 00:19:42,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Three Strikes! Batter Out!</font>

247
00:19:42,772 --> 00:19:46,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Game Over!</font>

248
00:19:46,505 --> 00:19:49,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? That's it?</font>

249
00:20:06,972 --> 00:20:10,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara could have gone a bit easy on me.</font>

250
00:20:24,072 --> 00:20:28,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Where is my uniform?</font>

251
00:20:28,205 --> 00:20:29,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Yoshikawa.</i></font>

252
00:20:31,705 --> 00:20:35,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This was on the hallway floor.
Is it yours?</font>

253
00:20:36,405 --> 00:20:39,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Did you drop your uniform, Nao?</font>

254
00:20:41,505 --> 00:20:46,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Perhaps... Thank you.</font>

255
00:20:46,572 --> 00:20:49,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, what's wrong with you?</font>

256
00:20:50,005 --> 00:20:53,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe this is all part of</font>

257
00:20:53,105 --> 00:20:54,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa's charm?</font>

258
00:20:54,839 --> 00:20:56,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so jealous of her feminine charms.</font>

259
00:20:56,872 --> 00:21:01,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Looks like Uehara is interested
in you as well.</font>

260
00:21:01,105 --> 00:21:02,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Really?</font>

261
00:21:04,105 --> 00:21:05,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, not at all.</font>

262
00:21:05,105 --> 00:21:07,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Bye then.
-See you around.</font>

263
00:21:13,605 --> 00:21:17,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Milk pudding or milk jelly...</font>

264
00:21:17,105 --> 00:21:19,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's so hard to choose between them.</font>

265
00:21:20,205 --> 00:21:22,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's such a tough choice.</font>

266
00:21:23,705 --> 00:21:28,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I love the richness of pudding,</font>

267
00:21:28,805 --> 00:21:33,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but I also love the smoothness of jelly.</font>

268
00:21:34,305 --> 00:21:36,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Which do you like better, Marina?</font>

269
00:21:37,972 --> 00:21:40,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What are you hiding?
-What?</font>

270
00:21:41,205 --> 00:21:42,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Whenever you hide things,</font>

271
00:21:42,905 --> 00:21:44,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you talk a whole bunch of crap,
over and over.</font>

272
00:21:46,305 --> 00:21:47,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

273
00:21:47,839 --> 00:21:50,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't mean to babble.</font>

274
00:22:00,205 --> 00:22:02,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait, Marina!</font>

275
00:22:05,705 --> 00:22:08,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina, wait!</font>

276
00:22:14,005 --> 00:22:16,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now, Marina...</font>

277
00:22:23,405 --> 00:22:25,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the hell?</font>

278
00:22:25,505 --> 00:22:28,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're living with a boy like this?</font>

279
00:22:28,939 --> 00:22:31,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It will take a bit to explain, but...</font>

280
00:22:33,005 --> 00:22:35,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You were hiding it from me too?</font>

281
00:22:41,839 --> 00:22:43,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

282
00:22:48,505 --> 00:22:50,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's the whole story.</font>

283
00:22:53,672 --> 00:22:57,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So we're not living together nor dating.</font>

284
00:22:58,205 --> 00:23:00,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm just waiting until a space
is available in the girls dorm.</font>

285
00:23:01,505 --> 00:23:03,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, who is it?</font>

286
00:23:04,305 --> 00:23:05,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

287
00:23:05,305 --> 00:23:07,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The guy you are living with?</font>

288
00:23:09,505 --> 00:23:13,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, it's...</font>

289
00:23:14,805 --> 00:23:16,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Older, same age? Which one?</font>

290
00:23:20,772 --> 00:23:24,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">About the same, I think.</font>

291
00:23:24,305 --> 00:23:29,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Same school? Do I know him?</font>

292
00:23:30,205 --> 00:23:32,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Daichi?</font>

293
00:23:32,405 --> 00:23:33,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not him, no.</font>

294
00:23:33,505 --> 00:23:35,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, not him.</font>

295
00:23:35,105 --> 00:23:38,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, better than him? Worse?</font>

296
00:23:39,072 --> 00:23:42,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Definitely worse...
I mean Daichi is one of the top three.</font>

297
00:23:44,105 --> 00:23:47,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well... I'm not sure.</font>

298
00:23:48,772 --> 00:23:49,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

299
00:23:51,805 --> 00:23:57,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Socially, he's actually above Daichi.</font>

300
00:23:57,872 --> 00:24:00,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Which means that...</font>

301
00:24:08,505 --> 00:24:10,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's Uehara!</font>

302
00:24:13,305 --> 00:24:15,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Welcome home.</font>

303
00:24:15,472 --> 00:24:17,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought you have part time job today.</font>

304
00:24:19,472 --> 00:24:20,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I finished early.</font>

305
00:24:20,872 --> 00:24:24,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I see.</font>

306
00:24:25,405 --> 00:24:28,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is my best friend, Marina.</font>

307
00:24:41,405 --> 00:24:45,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of all days, why today...</font>

308
00:24:51,205 --> 00:24:52,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Go.</font>

309
00:24:56,205 --> 00:24:57,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Darn it all!</font>

310
00:25:10,672 --> 00:25:12,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry that I kept it a secret.</font>

311
00:25:13,972 --> 00:25:15,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao!</font>

312
00:25:16,505 --> 00:25:17,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

313
00:25:21,205 --> 00:25:23,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is amazing!</font>

314
00:25:23,505 --> 00:25:25,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sit down, sit down.</font>

315
00:25:25,205 --> 00:25:26,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is so amazing.</font>

316
00:25:26,505 --> 00:25:30,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can get close
to the incredible Uehara.</font>

317
00:25:30,505 --> 00:25:31,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If I come to your house,</font>

318
00:25:32,039 --> 00:25:35,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can meet him anytime, right?</font>

319
00:25:35,672 --> 00:25:37,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I guess yes,</font>

320
00:25:37,705 --> 00:25:40,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but he is usually at work, not home.</font>

321
00:25:41,772 --> 00:25:43,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, Nao, how do you feel about him?</font>

322
00:25:44,105 --> 00:25:45,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">About what?</font>

323
00:25:45,305 --> 00:25:48,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You don't feel anything for Uehara?</font>

324
00:25:49,605 --> 00:25:52,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nothing actually.</font>

325
00:25:52,305 --> 00:25:53,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

326
00:25:54,105 --> 00:25:55,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nothing at all.</font>

327
00:25:55,605 --> 00:25:58,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If that's the case, can you help me?
Please! Set me up with him!</font>

328
00:26:01,305 --> 00:26:03,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess I can try,</font>

329
00:26:04,105 --> 00:26:07,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but Uehara is not the guy you think he is.</font>

330
00:26:08,872 --> 00:26:10,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're not even listening.</font>

331
00:26:10,872 --> 00:26:13,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, what? Yay!</font>

332
00:26:14,572 --> 00:26:16,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yay!</font>

333
00:26:18,672 --> 00:26:21,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-See you then.
-OK, see you tomorrow.</font>

334
00:26:30,772 --> 00:26:33,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't understand
why she likes him so much.</font>

335
00:26:35,572 --> 00:26:38,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Crap, you scared me!</font>

336
00:26:46,205 --> 00:26:48,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He didn't hear me, did he?</font>

337
00:26:51,839 --> 00:26:52,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

338
00:26:55,205 --> 00:26:56,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you thinking?</font>

339
00:27:02,105 --> 00:27:03,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do you mean?</font>

340
00:27:03,205 --> 00:27:05,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Living together.
If we get found out, we'll be expelled!</font>

341
00:27:08,805 --> 00:27:09,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know--</font>

342
00:27:09,839 --> 00:27:12,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, you don't, that's why you brought her!</font>

343
00:27:12,305 --> 00:27:13,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Listen to me--</font>

344
00:27:13,705 --> 00:27:16,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Keep her quiet, OK?</font>

345
00:27:23,205 --> 00:27:25,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina's not like that.</font>

346
00:27:26,205 --> 00:27:28,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-How do you know?
-I just know.</font>

347
00:27:28,505 --> 00:27:31,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's been my friend since junior high.</font>

348
00:27:33,705 --> 00:27:34,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Friend...</font>

349
00:27:36,105 --> 00:27:36,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do you mean?</font>

350
00:27:37,072 --> 00:27:38,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't trust her.</font>

351
00:27:38,705 --> 00:27:39,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

352
00:27:39,672 --> 00:27:42,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your friends are just like you.
Totally absent minded.</font>

353
00:27:48,072 --> 00:27:48,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, you!</font>

354
00:27:49,039 --> 00:27:50,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina is</font>

355
00:27:50,972 --> 00:27:53,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">totally different from me.</font>

356
00:27:53,705 --> 00:27:57,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's serious and strong.
You don't have to worry about her!</font>

357
00:27:58,505 --> 00:28:02,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You don't even know Marina,
but you say you don't trust her.</font>

358
00:28:03,605 --> 00:28:05,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's not fair.</font>

359
00:28:10,305 --> 00:28:15,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina is a friend I trust the most!</font>

360
00:28:23,305 --> 00:28:26,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What a complete jerk!</font>

361
00:28:28,805 --> 00:28:30,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I hate you!</i></font>

362
00:29:33,005 --> 00:29:35,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">MEGUROGAOKA HIGH SCHOOL</font>

363
00:29:39,972 --> 00:29:41,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the fuck?</font>

364
00:29:59,105 --> 00:30:01,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stay away from Uehara Hisashi.</font>

365
00:30:27,105 --> 00:30:28,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where are you going?</font>

366
00:30:29,605 --> 00:30:30,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The toilet.</font>

367
00:30:54,972 --> 00:30:57,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa, what are you doing?</font>

368
00:30:58,205 --> 00:31:00,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so sorry.</font>

369
00:31:00,605 --> 00:31:03,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, are you OK?</font>

370
00:31:03,572 --> 00:31:04,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

371
00:31:09,105 --> 00:31:10,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

372
00:31:10,605 --> 00:31:11,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

373
00:31:13,905 --> 00:31:16,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Something's up this morning.</font>

374
00:31:19,039 --> 00:31:20,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're not yourself.</font>

375
00:31:20,839 --> 00:31:21,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

376
00:31:21,872 --> 00:31:24,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did something happen with Uehara?</font>

377
00:31:24,505 --> 00:31:27,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, that's not it.</font>

378
00:31:27,939 --> 00:31:30,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm just a bit hungry. That's all.</font>

379
00:31:30,705 --> 00:31:33,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Really?
-Yes, really.</font>

380
00:31:35,605 --> 00:31:39,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When you are not smiling,
it really upsets me, you know.</font>

381
00:31:41,205 --> 00:31:42,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks, Marina.</font>

382
00:31:42,972 --> 00:31:45,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No problem.</font>

383
00:31:45,805 --> 00:31:47,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, dear...</font>

384
00:31:53,872 --> 00:31:56,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa, someone's calling for you.</font>

385
00:31:56,839 --> 00:31:58,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who?</font>

386
00:31:58,605 --> 00:32:01,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara. He's waiting in the PE hall.</font>

387
00:32:05,305 --> 00:32:09,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really? Thanks.</font>

388
00:32:11,772 --> 00:32:14,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe she's really popular?</font>

389
00:32:15,305 --> 00:32:16,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Well...
-Huh?</font>

390
00:32:17,405 --> 00:32:19,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why would he call for me at school?</font>

391
00:32:20,039 --> 00:32:21,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What did I do wrong this time?</font>

392
00:32:26,505 --> 00:32:28,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara?</font>

393
00:32:30,905 --> 00:32:33,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where is he?</font>

394
00:32:40,305 --> 00:32:41,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

395
00:32:41,405 --> 00:32:44,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry, we tricked you.</font>

396
00:32:54,039 --> 00:32:55,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no escape, you know.</font>

397
00:32:55,972 --> 00:32:58,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, what is it between you and Uehara?</font>

398
00:32:59,305 --> 00:33:00,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

399
00:33:00,405 --> 00:33:02,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stop pretending, spit it out!</font>

400
00:33:04,205 --> 00:33:06,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't pretend that you don't know</font>

401
00:33:07,105 --> 00:33:09,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">the rules about Uehara Hisashi.</font>

402
00:33:19,005 --> 00:33:21,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stay away from Uehara Hisashi.</font>

403
00:33:27,472 --> 00:33:30,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, why are you here, Uehara?</font>

404
00:33:30,605 --> 00:33:31,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

405
00:33:33,305 --> 00:33:37,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara is for everyone, OK?</font>

406
00:33:37,105 --> 00:33:38,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You got it?</font>

407
00:33:38,205 --> 00:33:41,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And you're not really good enough
to fit in with us though.</font>

408
00:33:41,105 --> 00:33:42,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's right.</font>

409
00:33:43,839 --> 00:33:48,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm amazed you have the guts
to meet Uehara with that face and body.</font>

410
00:33:58,305 --> 00:34:00,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Even though he is so cool and perfect,</i></font>

411
00:34:00,905 --> 00:34:04,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">he has a big scar on his heart.</font>

412
00:34:05,205 --> 00:34:09,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-That is Uehara.
-Poor Uehara.</font>

413
00:34:09,705 --> 00:34:13,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But we all are always by his side.</font>

414
00:34:13,705 --> 00:34:17,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're kindly watching over him.</font>

415
00:34:17,605 --> 00:34:19,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That is our reason for living.</font>

416
00:34:19,772 --> 00:34:22,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-That's right.
-Yep, she's right.</font>

417
00:34:22,839 --> 00:34:25,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He absolutely needs us.</font>

418
00:34:25,672 --> 00:34:27,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're so right.</font>

419
00:34:27,305 --> 00:34:29,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't think he needs that.</font>

420
00:34:30,905 --> 00:34:31,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-Huh?</font>

421
00:34:34,772 --> 00:34:37,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's not <i>poor Uehara, you know.</i></font>

422
00:34:40,472 --> 00:34:42,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>He doesn't need you.</i></font>

423
00:34:44,072 --> 00:34:47,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? What are you saying?</font>

424
00:34:47,505 --> 00:34:50,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Uehara lost his parents--
-I know!</font>

425
00:34:52,105 --> 00:34:53,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know that,</font>

426
00:34:55,305 --> 00:34:59,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but when someone is doing his best,</font>

427
00:34:59,939 --> 00:35:02,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you should say, <i>well done,
not <i>poor you, right?</i></i></font>

428
00:35:07,772 --> 00:35:10,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your rules are so stupid.</font>

429
00:35:11,105 --> 00:35:12,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-Huh?</font>

430
00:35:13,405 --> 00:35:15,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You keep saying you know him</font>

431
00:35:15,405 --> 00:35:18,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">because of his looks and this and that,</font>

432
00:35:19,939 --> 00:35:22,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but if you really want to get
to know someone,</font>

433
00:35:23,872 --> 00:35:26,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You should talk, laugh and fight with him.</font>

434
00:35:26,872 --> 00:35:30,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Without doing that, how could you know?</font>

435
00:35:33,305 --> 00:35:36,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">For those who don't even know that,</font>

436
00:35:38,005 --> 00:35:40,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara won't even express
the slightest interest!</font>

437
00:35:55,839 --> 00:35:57,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, dear, I said it all.</font>

438
00:35:59,472 --> 00:36:02,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right, now you've pissed me off.</font>

439
00:36:03,039 --> 00:36:04,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who the fuck are you?</font>

440
00:36:05,072 --> 00:36:06,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Fuck off.</font>

441
00:36:27,105 --> 00:36:28,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Uehara?
-Uehara?</font>

442
00:36:39,772 --> 00:36:43,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You, you are just so stupid.</font>

443
00:36:45,405 --> 00:36:46,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

444
00:37:02,105 --> 00:37:04,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She is my girlfriend.</font>

445
00:37:05,672 --> 00:37:06,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

446
00:37:07,672 --> 00:37:09,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When you have a problem, tell me.</font>

447
00:37:10,305 --> 00:37:13,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-No way...
-You're lying.</font>

448
00:37:13,505 --> 00:37:15,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara?</font>

449
00:37:17,805 --> 00:37:19,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's go.</font>

450
00:37:30,772 --> 00:37:32,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey...</font>

451
00:37:33,905 --> 00:37:35,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

452
00:37:35,305 --> 00:37:38,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why are you doing this?</font>

453
00:37:38,705 --> 00:37:40,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Me and you--</font>

454
00:37:40,171 --> 00:37:43,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Be quiet. Just walk, OK?</font>

455
00:37:43,872 --> 00:37:45,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

456
00:37:45,205 --> 00:37:48,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh my God!</font>

457
00:37:58,105 --> 00:37:59,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao?</font>

458
00:38:13,405 --> 00:38:14,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

459
00:38:14,405 --> 00:38:16,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No one's looking now, right?</font>

460
00:38:17,405 --> 00:38:18,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

461
00:38:19,405 --> 00:38:21,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought it over again.</font>

462
00:38:21,305 --> 00:38:24,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I realized pretending to be strangers
was impossible.</font>

463
00:38:24,572 --> 00:38:28,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If we pretend to go out, I have a reason
to go to your house, right?</font>

464
00:38:28,939 --> 00:38:30,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, what you're saying is...</font>

465
00:38:30,605 --> 00:38:32,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's pretend to be going out.</font>

466
00:38:33,072 --> 00:38:33,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Pretend?</i></font>

467
00:38:34,105 --> 00:38:37,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, sorry, did I get your hopes up?</font>

468
00:38:40,205 --> 00:38:43,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, not really.</font>

469
00:38:46,972 --> 00:38:48,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, so you want to really go out then?</font>

470
00:38:56,872 --> 00:38:58,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Got you!</font>

471
00:39:02,772 --> 00:39:05,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I've got to go to work. Bye.</font>

472
00:39:09,572 --> 00:39:11,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara,</font>

473
00:39:17,672 --> 00:39:19,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">thank you</font>

474
00:39:20,405 --> 00:39:22,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">for saving me.</font>

475
00:39:30,072 --> 00:39:31,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

476
00:39:32,105 --> 00:39:33,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

477
00:39:33,572 --> 00:39:34,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">About yesterday.</font>

478
00:39:35,905 --> 00:39:37,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">About your friend.</font>

479
00:39:39,405 --> 00:39:42,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, that... yeah.</font>

480
00:39:47,872 --> 00:39:49,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Go back quickly or you'll catch a cold!</font>

481
00:39:52,605 --> 00:39:53,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay.</font>

482
00:40:01,705 --> 00:40:03,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara?</font>

483
00:40:05,939 --> 00:40:07,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara!</font>

484
00:40:07,305 --> 00:40:09,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, are you OK?</font>

485
00:40:09,772 --> 00:40:12,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Uehara...</font>

486
00:40:21,105 --> 00:40:22,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">MEGUROGAOKA SAKURA HOSPITAL</font>

487
00:40:30,205 --> 00:40:33,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't worry, he's just tired from work
and not enough sleep.</font>

488
00:40:33,572 --> 00:40:36,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe he was just a bit undernourished.</font>

489
00:40:37,305 --> 00:40:39,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If he eats properly, and rests
for a few days, he'll be fine.</font>

490
00:40:40,605 --> 00:40:43,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you so much.</font>

491
00:40:54,505 --> 00:40:57,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I've gotten in touch with his family too.</i></font>

492
00:40:57,772 --> 00:40:59,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Take care.</font>

493
00:41:07,505 --> 00:41:08,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara?</font>

494
00:41:11,005 --> 00:41:12,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh.</font>

495
00:41:13,505 --> 00:41:17,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Oh?" I was really worried about you.</font>

496
00:41:18,005 --> 00:41:20,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's because you sleep on the couch.</font>

497
00:41:20,705 --> 00:41:23,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're exaggerating, it's nothing.</font>

498
00:41:23,405 --> 00:41:24,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nothing?</font>

499
00:41:25,005 --> 00:41:26,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right, let's go home.</font>

500
00:41:26,505 --> 00:41:27,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

501
00:41:27,572 --> 00:41:31,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, take it easy.</font>

502
00:41:31,205 --> 00:41:33,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll be fine if I eat something yummy.</font>

503
00:41:33,405 --> 00:41:34,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

504
00:41:56,205 --> 00:41:57,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri.</font>

505
00:42:04,972 --> 00:42:06,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Yuri?</i></font>

506
00:42:07,705 --> 00:42:09,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>So she's Uehara's girlfriend?</i></font>

507
00:43:41,105 --> 00:43:44,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THIS IS A FICTIONAL DRAMA.</font>
